lead_paragraph: Australia's Rebecca Wiasak overwhelmed Poland's Malgorzata Wojtyra to retain her individual pursuit title as the world track championships began at London's velodrome on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Australian Wiasak Retains World Pursuit Title
